<!-- Content Section -->
<div class="membership-content">
    <h1>Become a Member</h1>
    
    <h2>Why Join Mountain Forum Himalayas?</h2>
    <p>As a member, you will actively contribute to the vision and mission of Mountain Forum Himalayas (MFH), working towards the sustainable development and protection of the Himalayan regions. Your involvement will help shape the future of local governance, disaster risk reduction, livelihood promotion, and environmental conservation.</p>
    
    <h2>Benefits of Membership</h2>
    <p>Members of MFH will be engaged in various committees, have opportunities to collaborate on community-driven projects, and play a pivotal role in protecting the rights of marginalized communities in the Himalayan regions. You will also have the opportunity to participate in conferences, workshops, and coordination meetings with state and district authorities.</p>
    
